tedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:51:10.000Z","msg":"佢哋唔認自己係香港人，就唔係香港人，不過我覺得唔一定要識講廣東話先係香港人<br />\n最緊要係認同價值同貢獻香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/topic/1024x576/201908/20190809112738_1_2019-aug-9-001.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Ftopic%2F1024x576%2F201908%2F20190809112738_1_2019-aug-9-001.jpg&h=f0003698&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"03130161ef94c6a40a12307748fdf22dc154e8b5","tid":1600749,"uid":15823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:54:39.000Z","msg":"如果真係中國人一早都講左我係中國人啦<br />\n香港人呢個term 就唔會出現<br />\n就係兩者唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42f2f6019c7489541d615e21ced87555d6246759","tid":1600749,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:56:19.000Z","msg":"只要我哋不斷強化香港人獨特身份同價值觀，強調香港身份既包容性<br />\n就算唔提港獨，西方都會自然將香港人同中國人區別起黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b07237572dd7d39f3a261f24b890eaf94bb4d178","tid":1600749,"uid":15620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T18:02:23.000Z","msg":"佢地講講下就會講到骨子裡、血統上係中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69855b48ba2c88ea134ae9e76052b4f210a17f58","tid":1600749,"uid":124180,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T18:06:35.000Z","msg":"之前睇過篇文講過差唔多概念既嘢 講中國式國家主義同西方國家主義既中心思想係互不相容<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7a68ddd62f7cb4fadc7d8b7bd2a3546a9984a3d","tid":1600749,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T03:45:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad3f00d4a95160e3414863e53f15735887de4977","tid":1600749,"uid":254246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit